headline: Dow Jones Futures Loom; Nvidia, Meta, Tesla Near Buy Zones With Fed Meeting Ahead
summary: The stock market rally is at highs, with Tesla racing while Nvidia and Meta set up. The Federal Reserve meeting looms.
